                    <description>&lt;p&gt;the patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/50240&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/50240&lt;/a&gt; demonstrates that number of tests don&apos;t really hit fail_loc they set, meaning they are useless:&lt;/p&gt;

